rch-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-c-6.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55r2-c-6","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":3,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55r2-c-6-1781761364358-6qni37","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-c-6-1781761364358-6qni37\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-c-6-1781761364358-6qni37\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55r2-c-6-1781761364358-6qni37\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 227,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781762964664,"end":1781762971105}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0e841487fdf3a422016a338b88e2dc8191bb32186ee62cc0db"}},"id":"prt_ed9590ed00014QwlQ7sHsBompC","sessionID":"ses_126a7351cffe2yu58i7OdmNdV8","messageID":"msg_ed958cf2e001Fpm11aiNR6YWoG"}}
