{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763028187,"sessionID":"ses_126a7351cffe2yu58i7OdmNdV8","part":{"id":"prt_ed95a2093001Mk0hg9NdLt88is","messageID":"msg_ed95a10510018QM3UZ4g5zkxWv","sessionID":"ses_126a7351cffe2yu58i7OdmNdV8","type":"text","text":"The lineage is a single-iteration review capped by `maxIterations: 1`, so synthesis will be terminal by hard cap rather than full four-dimension convergence unless the first pass finds a blocker. Next I’m resolving the actual C-rest-of-server scope and existing lineage state.","time":{"start":1781763022995,"end":1781763028186},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_01a8a30e91d2bd18016a338bcef5e481918ea48f1e82a0aac8","phase":"commentary"}}}}
