{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763102339,"sessionID":"ses_126a7351cffe2yu58i7OdmNdV8","part":{"id":"prt_ed95b4b38001zUp800WE3QFyB1","messageID":"msg_ed95b03ee001DTWYNiAnlo3ABU","sessionID":"ses_126a7351cffe2yu58i7OdmNdV8","type":"text","text":"The direct server IPC wrapper delegates security-sensitive socket binding to `@spec-kit/shared/ipc/socket-server.js`, so I’m opening that shared implementation before deciding whether socket-dir issues are real findings or already guarded.","time":{"start":1781763099448,"end":1781763102337},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0625282103302723016a338c1b68188191a42f83c03d166653","phase":"commentary"}}}}
