{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763218007,"sessionID":"ses_126a7351cffe2yu58i7OdmNdV8","part":{"id":"prt_ed95d02f0001eWGybo0An94Yxr","messageID":"msg_ed95cdefb001PX4aV39FNjTzn9","sessionID":"ses_126a7351cffe2yu58i7OdmNdV8","type":"text","text":"The `memory_save` replay behavior is not accidental: tests assert it as replayable, and README documents the same secondary-index gap. I’ll treat it as an active data-integrity risk rather than an inference-only bug.","time":{"start":1781763212016,"end":1781763218004},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_03a14b1c6d665a2c016a338c8be4448191ba3b610fd2ff937d","phase":"commentary"}}}}
