ations: 1` as hard-cap terminal synthesis, not full convergence.\n- Focus first pass on daemon lifecycle, IPC trust, reconnect/replay, and fail-closed behavior per scope emphasis.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Confirm exact line evidence for both candidate findings.\n- Write `deep-review-config.json`, `deep-review-state.jsonl`, `iterations/iteration-001.md`.\n- Generate `deep-review-findings-registry.json`, `deep-review-dashboard.md`, `deep-review-strategy.md`.\n- Write `review-report.md`.\n- Return `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55r2-c-6`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Memory trigger with supplied session failed: `Error: sessionId \"fanout-gpt55r2-c-6-1781761364358-6qni37\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.`\n- Retried memory trigger without session binding; no matching trigger phrases.\n- Scope path: `.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server`.\n- Candidate 1 evidence includes `ENV_REFERENCE.md` line 180, `spec-memory.cjs` line 112, `launcher-ipc-bridge.cjs` line 81, `model-server-supervision.cjs` line 444.\n- Candidate 2 evidence includes `.opencode/bin/lib/launcher-session-proxy.cjs` lines 33-47 and 146-152.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md`: workflow contract.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server/spec.md`: review scope.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/rev